---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Haunted House Toronto">
  <main>
    <div class="bg-haunted-orange flex py-24 md:py-32 text-white px-8">
      <div class="flex-col max-w-[800px] mx-auto flex-auto space-y-8">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mx-auto px-auto">
          <a href="https://hackclub.com"> Hack Club Presents</a>
        </h3>

        <h1
          class="font-fright text-orange-100 text-6xl 2xs:text-7xl xs:text-8xl md:text-9xl"
        >
          Haunted House<br />
           Toronto
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-xl 2xs:text-2xl xs:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium">
          A Halloween-themed mini-hackathon for high-schoolers in Toronto.
        </h2>

        <div class="flex space-x-1 2xs:space-x-2 md:space-x-3">
          <svg
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            clip-rule="evenodd"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-miterlimit="1.414"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            aria-label="event-code"
            viewBox="0 0 32 32"
            preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="inline -mt-1 h-[38px] w-[38px] xs:h-[46px] xs:w-[46px] md:h-[52px] md:w-[52px]"
          >
            <g>
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
                d="M28 16C28 6 26 4 16 4S4 6 4 16s2 12 12 12 12-2 12-12zm-3.664 8.336C25.425 23.247 26 21.1 26 16c0-2.14-.101-3.76-.3-5H6.3C6.1 12.24 6 13.86 6 16c0 5.1.575 7.247 1.664 8.336C8.753 25.425 10.9 26 16 26s7.247-.575 8.336-1.664zM11 8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h8a1 1 0 0 1 0 2h-8a1 1 0 0 1-1-1z"
              ></path>
              <path
                d="M9.082 19.325c-.157-.209-.332-.49-.332-.825 0-.335.175-.617.332-.826h.001c.849-1.104 1.978-1.963 3.077-2.798l.01-.008.546-.418a.976.976 0 0 1 1.31.114.86.86 0 0 1-.121 1.265c-.18.14-.362.277-.543.415-.925.706-1.842 1.404-2.576 2.256.725.838 1.659 1.552 2.579 2.256.181.139.362.276.54.415a.859.859 0 0 1 .121 1.265.976.976 0 0 1-1.31.113h-.001l-.183-.142-.079-.06-.268-.205-.003-.002c-1.097-.837-2.264-1.728-3.099-2.814l-.001-.002zM22.918 19.325c.157-.209.332-.49.332-.825 0-.335-.175-.617-.332-.826h-.001c-.849-1.104-1.978-1.963-3.077-2.798a89.607 89.607 0 0 1-.556-.425.976.976 0 0 0-1.31.112.86.86 0 0 0 .121 1.266c.18.14.361.277.541.415h.002c.925.706 1.842 1.404 2.576 2.256-.725.838-1.659 1.552-2.579 2.256-.181.139-.362.276-.54.415a.859.859 0 0 0-.121 1.265.976.976 0 0 0 1.31.113h.001l.53-.407.003-.002c1.097-.837 2.264-1.728 3.099-2.814l.001-.002z"
              ></path>
            </g></svg
          >

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <p
              class="inline my-auto text-lg 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl md:text-3xl"
            >
              November 4th, 10:00 am to 4:30 pm
            </p>

            <p
              class="inline my-auto text-lg 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl md:text-3xl"
            >
              <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/MzQbL7NqjuwFwCpz8"
                >Northern District Library (at Yonge/Eglinton)
              </a>
            </p>

            <a href="https://tally.so/r/mVP17N" target="_blank">
              <p
                class="text-lg pr-4 px-4 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl lg:text-3xl bg-black text-white py-2 xs:py-4 w-full text-center border-[3px] xs:border-4 border-haunted-orange motion-safe:active:text-trillium-yellow"
              >
                Register
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col max-w-[800px] p-8 xs:py-24 md:py-32 mx-auto flex-auto space-y-10 xs:space-y-16 md:space-y-20"
    >
      <div class="space-y-2 xs:space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
        <h3
          class="font-fright text-2xl 2xs:text-3xl xs:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
        >
          What is it?
        </h3>

        <p class="text-lg 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium">
          Haunted House Toronto is an in-person free event where high schoolers
          will come together <span class="text-haunted-orange"
            >regardless of experience</span
          > for a day of <span class="font-wack text-red-500 align-bottom"
            >learning</span
          >, <span class="font-wack text-blue-500 align-bottom">making</span>
           and having <span class="font-wack text-violet-600 align-bottom"
            >fun</span
          >. You'll get the chance to make games and websites, your imagination is
          your limit! At the end, we'll be making rooms for a virtual haunted
          house for your projects!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 xs:space-y-8 md:space-y-10 lg:space-y-14">
        <div class="space-y-2 xs:space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
          <h3
            class="font-fright text-2xl 2xs:text-3xl xs:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
          >
            Interested?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium">
            Join us! We'd love to have you at Haunted House Toronto!
          </p>

          <div>
            <a href="https://tally.so/r/mVP17N" target="_blank">
              <p
                class="text-lg px-4 2xs:text-xl xs:text-2xl lg:text-3xl bg-haunted-orange text-white py-2 xs:py-4 w-full text-center motion-safe:active:text-trillium-yellow"
              >
                Register
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="font-fright text-2xl 2xs:text-3xl xs:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">FAQ</h3>

        <h4 class="text-2xl">Who's running this?</h4>
        <p>
          We're a group of teenagers, supported by Hack Club, a 501(c)(3)
          nonprofit global network (based in the U.S.) and a network of
          student-led coding clubs and high school makers. Founded in 2014, Hack
          Clubs are now in nearly 400 high schools with 10,000 students each
          year. Last May, we also ran <a
            class="text-orange-700 font-bold"
            href="https://https://hack.af/angelhacks-tophoto"
            >AngelHacks Toronto</a
          >, a game jam for 50 highschoolers in the GTA
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-2xl">What is hacking?</h4>
        <p>
          No, we're not “hacking” bank accounts. Hacking is a term for coding
          apps, games, websites etc. It's safe and entirely educational.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-2xl">Will there be food & supervision?</h4>
        <p>
          There will be free food and refreshments. Workshops and activities
          will be held throughout the event. Adult supervision will be present
          at all times with access restricted to participants.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="font-fright text-2xl 2xs:text-3xl xs:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Photos from AngelHacks Toronto</h3>

        <img
          src="https://cloud-pa5cw6l98-hack-club-bot.vercel.app/0image.png"
        />
        <img
          src="https://cloud-a9hrey1fv-hack-club-bot.vercel.app/0image.png"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="flex px-8 text-center py-2 xs:py-4 text-xs md:text-base">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto flex-auto">
        <p>
          This site is open-sourced on <a
            class="hover:underline"
            href="https://github.com/hackclub/hauntedhouse-toronto/"
            target="_blank">GitHub</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          Made with <span class="text-pink-500">❤</span> by Sam Liu and Arav
          Narula
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
